{"operationName":"pairs","variables":{"allPairs":["0xd84b7a96f7de5088810339a41f912d7eaca19b30","0xe97f10c499b0e37438bb815608d4a2cc723a2841","0x11d742b97d4de0a64740083fd9b68b0a268654ef"]},"query":"fragment PairFields on Pair {

  token0 {
    id
    symbol
    name
    totalLiquidity
    derivedETH
    __typename
  }
  token1 {
    id
    symbol
    name
    totalLiquidity

query pairs($allPairs: [Bytes]!) {
  pairs(where: {id_in: $allPairs}, orderBy: trackedReserveETH, orderDirection: desc) {
    ...PairFields
    __typename
  }
}
"}
